---
// /welcome — pre-auth landing page that explains the three access tiers
// before the user clicks through to Cloudflare Access OTP. Linked to from
// the dashboard's 「登录」 button. Public path (not under /internal/*),
// so Cloudflare Access doesn't intercept it.
//
// Authenticated users won't normally end up here (the dashboard swaps the
// 「登录」 button for their name once auth resolves), but if they navigate
// directly we still show the same content so the page is always self-
// explanatory.
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>登录 — 新东方前途出国苏州分公司内部看板</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #042f24;
        --primary-dim: #0a4535;
        --surface: #fafafa;
        --surface-raised: #ffffff;
        --hairline: #eef0f3;
        --text: #0f172a;
        --text-muted: #64748b;
        --text-soft: #94a3b8;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: var(--surface);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
        font-feature-settings: 'cv11';
        min-height: 100vh;
      }
      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      .font-headline { font-family: 'Manrope', 'Inter', sans-serif; }

      .wrap {
        max-width: 640px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 80px 24px 48px;
      }
      .logo {
        font-family: 'Manrope', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 36px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin: 0 0 16px;
      }
      .lede {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0 0 32px;
      }

      .tier {
        background: var(--surface-raised);
        border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 18px 22px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.025);
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .tier__num {
        flex-shrink: 0;
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: rgba(4, 47, 36, 0.08);
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 1px;
      }
      .tier__body { flex: 1; }
      .tier__title {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14.5px;
        margin: 0 0 4px;
        color: var(--text);
        letter-spacing: -0.005em;
      }
      .tier__desc {
        font-size: 13.5px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin: 0;
      }

      .cta-row {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-top: 32px;
      }
      .cta {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 12px 22px;
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14px;
        transition: background 120ms ease;
      }
      .cta:hover { background: var(--primary-dim); }
      .cta-secondary {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .cta-secondary:hover { color: var(--text); }

      .contact {
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 24px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--text-soft);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
      .contact strong {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .contact a {
        color: var(--primary);
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <div class="logo">SUZHOU XDF · INTERNAL</div>

      <h1 class="font-headline">新东方前途出国苏州分公司<br />中期看板</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        登录前请先了解你的访问权限。下面三档对应不同的邮箱身份，登录后系统会自动识别。
      </p>

      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier__num">1</div>
        <div class="tier__body">
          <h3 class="tier__title">新东方邮箱（@xdf.cn）</h3>
          <p class="tier__desc">
            可以阅读 dashboard、学生总览，无法编辑、无法看任何顾问的日报、无法提交沟通记录。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier__num">2</div>
        <div class="tier__body">
          <h3 class="tier__title">在职中期顾问</h3>
          <p class="tier__desc">
            在第一档基础上，可以提交名下学生的最新沟通情况入库，可以查看自己的每日工作日报。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tier">
        <div class="tier__num">3</div>
        <div class="tier__body">
          <h3 class="tier__title">管理员</h3>
          <p class="tier__desc">
            完整权限，包括 inbox 审核、所有顾问的日报。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="/internal/students" class="cta">
          进入看板 →
        </a>
        <a href="/internal" class="cta-secondary">先看公开 dashboard</a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact">
        <strong>登录方式</strong>：点击「进入看板」后，系统会发送一次性验证码到你的邮箱。<br />
        <strong>其他情况</strong>：联系王世杰 <a href="mailto:wangshijie11@xdf.cn">wangshijie11@xdf.cn</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
